    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-03-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-03-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="1610"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1610">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 819.77/107.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-03-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 5, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Dziuk concession has been revoked by the Government of Panama, on the ground
                    of failure to fulfill certain of its terms. See my No. 15 of November 29,
                    1911.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dodge.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
